<div class="allowance">
    <div class="top">
        <p><span>注意：</span>新建津贴确定后，需对页面进行保存更新才能立即生效，保存更新后请重新核对工资单。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="conShow">
    </div>



    <div class="set">
        <div class="content1">
            <div class="name">
                <span>津贴名称</span>
                <input type="text" class="allowanceName" placeholder="请输入津贴名称">
            </div>
            <div class="remark">
                <span >备注</span>
                <input class="remark1" type="text" placeholder="请输入备注信息">
            </div>
            <div class="money">
                <span class="money1">金额</span>
                <input class="money2" type="text" placeholder="请输入金额">
                <span class="money3">元</span>
                <div class="month">每月</div>
            </div>
            <div class="money" style="height:40px;"></div>
            <div class="monthSelect">
                <ul>
                    <li class="monthSelect1">每月</li>
                    <li>每出勤日</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="content2">
            <div class="scope">
                <span style="float:left;">适合出勤范围：</span>
                <div class="img">
                    <img class="img1" src="#springUrl('/resource/img/Switch-OFF.png')" style="display: inline;">
                    <img class="img2" src="#springUrl('/resource/img/Switch-ON.png')" style="display: none;">
                </div>
                <span>&nbsp;缺勤天数大于</span>
                <input class="dataText" type="text" value="0">
                <span>天时，不享受该津贴</span>
            </div>
            <div class="type">
                <div class="span1">适合类型：</div>
                <div class="dept"><input  class="just" type="checkbox">&nbsp;正式</div>
                <div class="dept1"><input class="service" type="checkbox">&nbsp;劳务</div>
                <div class="span2">（针对下方所选择的部门及员工）</div>
            </div>
            <div class="formcCheckbox">
                <div class="span3">
                    <div class="span3Inp1"><input type="checkbox" />&nbsp;转正</div>
                    <div class="span3Inp2"><input type="checkbox" />&nbsp;试用期</div>
                </div>
                <div class="span33">
                    <div class="span33Inp1"><input type="checkbox" />&nbsp;转正</div>
                    <div class="span33Inp2"><input type="checkbox" />&nbsp;试用期</div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="type">
                <div class="tryOut">适用部门及员工</div>
                <div class="tryShow"></div>
            </div>
            <div class="type" style="height:40px;">
                <div class="tryOutAdd">添加</div>
            </div>

            <div class="save">保存</div>
            <div class="cancel">取消</div>
        </div>


        <div class="trySeek">
            <div id="container">
                <div id="content">
                    <div class="first"><input id="kw" onKeyup="getContent(this);" placeholder="请输入员工姓名"/></div>
                    <div id="append"></div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <img class="trySeekImg" src="#springUrl('/resource/img/guanbi.png')" alt="">
            <div class="trySeekCont">

            </div>
        </div>
        <img class="previewImg" src="#springUrl('/resource/img/wenhao.png')" alt="" title="每月：每月固定发放金额数
每出勤日：出勤日/计薪日*金额数">
    </div>
    <div class="btn"><img src="#springUrl('/resource/img/tianjia.png')" alt="">&nbsp;&nbsp;添加津贴</div>
</div>
<div class="bonus">
    <div class="top">
        <p><span>注意：</span>请在此处输入您需要的项目，也可从常用奖金类型中选取，选中后的奖金类型会出现在算工资的工资表格中。对该页面的修改将在保存后立即生效，保存后请重新核对工资单。</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bonusShow">
        <div class="bonusShow1">您需要的奖金类型：</div>
        <div class="add"></div>
        <div class="bonusShow2">
            <input class="inpShow2" type="text">
            <div class="imgShow2"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="bonusShow3"><img src="#springUrl('/resource/img/jia.png')" alt=""></div>
    </div>
    <div class="use">
        <div class="use1">常用奖金类型</div>
        <ul>
            <li>绩效奖金</li>
            <li>月度奖金</li>
            <li>季度奖金</li>
            <li>项目奖金</li>
            <li>销售奖金</li>
            <li>加班费</li>
            <li>提成</li>
            <li>研发奖金</li>
            <li>计件奖金</li>
            <li>业绩奖</li>
        </ul>
    </div>
</div>
<div class="footerBtn">
    <div class="footer_allowance">
        <div class="footerBtn1">保存更新</div>
        <div class="footerBtn2">取消</div>
